c: 18
v: 28
t: "Tabintin wonkii maa…óa kin wonndude e …ďen noddoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe hi…ďe faandii Jaati Makko Kin, wata gite maa …óe yawtu gaayi ma…ď…ďe hara hi…óa faandii cu…óaari ngurdan aduna, wota a …óofto on mo Men welsindini …ďernde mun gaayi jantagol Men o jokki belee…óe makko fiyaake makko on woni halkaare"